<plot>When Jack and Liz die on their wedding day, they discover that the Afterlife turns out to be a corporate world where the levels of Heaven &amp; Hell are connected by the elevator. Trapped in Hell, Jack must work his way up the corporate ladder to reunite with Liz in Heaven. As an executive, Liz plots to manipulate the system so that she can be with Jack. Even though death is not what they expected, they find what truly matters.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?571015</url></doc>
